He gave away, I can't ſay, how many thouſands of Catechiſms, many hundreds with Expoſitions upon them; neither did he conſine his Catechumeniſts to the Aſſemblies Catechiſm (though 
                  the Lord Primate of Armagh ſaid 'twas the beſt Extant
               ) but he gave very many of Doctor Cumber's, and the Principles of the Chriſtian Religion cleared, and confirmed by the Articles and Homilies of the Church of England by Mr. Thomas Adams.

